    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this E46-generation M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart lies the S54B32 power plant, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for an exceptionally broad power band and an 8,000 RPM redline. This chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS bulletproofing kit, mitigating common platform weak points. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry is maintained by upgraded bushings and performance-valved dampers, ensuring the turn-in remains sharp and communicative. Though it carries the honest patina of a well-loved driver\u2019s car, its mechanical vitals are synchronized and ready for the apex.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
