      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect blend of performance and comfort. The exterior maintains a high-gloss finish, showing only minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with responsible ownership. Inside, the cabin is clean and inviting; the upholstery is in great shape with no major wear, and all technological features\u2014from the premium sound system to the navigation\u2014are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and has been serviced at regular intervals, ensuring a dependable and quiet ride. The tires have significant tread life remaining, and the brakes feel firm and responsive. This is an excellent opportunity to own a reliable, high-quality vehicle that is ready for the road today.",
